 Thiopental, Remifentanil, Sodium oxybate, More', 'Major', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/9655/', '[1] "Product Information. Spravato (esketamine)." Janssen Pharmaceuticals, Titusville, NJ.', 1767369485);
